# The `X86MachineFunctionInfo` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/x86machinefunctioninfo">X86MachineFunctionInfo</a> - This class is derived from <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a> and contains private <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/x86">X86</a> target-specific information for each <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a>. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/x86machinefunctioninfo">X86MachineFunctionInfo</a> - This class is derived from <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a> and contains private <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/x86">X86</a> target-specific information for each <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a>.
